{t:Fun Kosev biz Kitev}


Fun Kosev biz Kitev
iz a brikele faranen
Avu der Bal-shem
Shpatsirn iz gegangen
   
Fun Kosev biz Kitev
Iz a taykhele faranen
Avu der Bal-shem
Zikh toyvlen iz gegangen
   
Fun Kosev biz Kitev
Iz a veldele faranen
Avu der Bal-shem
Oyf hisboydedes iz gegangen
   
Fun Kosev biz Kitev
Zaynen feygelekh faranen
Avu der Bal-shem
lernen shire iz gegangen


Between Kosev and Kitev
There is a little bridge
Where the Baal Shem
Would stroll

Between Kosev and Kitev
There is a little stream
 Where the Baal Shem
Would immerse

Between Kosev and Kitev
There is a little forest
  Where the Baal Shem
Would meditate alone

Between Kosev and Kitev
There are little birds
   From whom the Baal Shem
Would learn to sing [God's praises]

 

 

